{% comment %}
  ============================================================
  TEMPLATE: templates/page.bundle.liquid
  ============================================================
  This template renders the Bundle Builder as a full-page experience.

  Setup:
    1. Copy this file to your theme's templates/ folder.
    2. In Shopify Admin > Online Store > Pages, create a new page.
    3. Set the page Template to "page.bundle" in the right-hand sidebar.
    4. Publish and share the page URL with your customers.
  ============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<div class="page-width">
  {% section 'bundle-builder' %}
</div>
